    Verse: 18
  Source:
    Title: Yoga Vasistha
Tags:
  - Contentment
---
What is contentment? To renounce all craving for what is not obtained
unsought and to be satisfied with what comes unsought, without being elated
or depressed ever by them -- this is contentment.
